1d].</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|colwidth=30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Mo Brooks}}\n* [http://brooks.house.gov/ Congressman Mo Brooks] official U.S. House site\n* [http://mobrooksforcongress.com/ Mo Brooks for Congress]\n*{{Dmoz|Regional/North_America/United_States/Alabama/Government/Federal/US_House_of_Representatives/Mo_Brooks_%5BR-5%5D}}\n* {{CongLinks | congbio = B001274 | ballot = Mo_Brooks | nndb = 564/000266763 | votesmart = 121610 | govtrack = 412395 | natjournal = 1798 | opencong = 412395 | rollcall = 31389 | politifact = | fec = H0AL05163 | opensecrets = N00030910 | assets = mo-brooks | legistorm = 2724/Rep_Mo_Brooks_AL.html | followthemoney = 10238 | ontheissues = House/Mo_Brooks.htm | congress = mo-brooks/1987 | worldcat = | c-span = mobrooks | imdb = | bloomberg = | nyt = | washpo = gIQAdMkz6O }}\n\n{{S-start}}\n{{s-par|us-hs}}\n{{USRepSuccessionBox\n|state=Alabama\n|district=5\n|before=[[Parker Griffith]]\n|after=Incumbent|years=January 3, 2011 \u2013 present}}\n{{s-prec|usa}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Diane Black]]<br><small>R-[[Tennessee]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title='' [[List of current members of the United States House of Representatives by seniority|United States Representatives by seniority]]''|years=276th}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Larry Bucshon]]<br><small>R-[[Indiana]]}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{AL-FedRep}}\n\n{{Persondata <!-- Metadata: see [[Wikipedia:Persondata]]. -->\n| NAME              = Brooks, Mo\n| ALTERNATIVE NAMES = Morris Brooks\n| SHORT DESCRIPTION = American politician\n| DATE OF BIRTH     = April 29, 1954\n| PLACE OF BIRTH    = Charleston, South Carolina\n| DATE OF DEATH     =\n| PLACE OF DEATH    =\n}}\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Brooks, Mo}}\n[[Category:1954 births]]\n[[Category:Alabama Republicans]]\n[[Category:American lawyers]]\n[[Category:Converts to Mormonism]]\n[[Category:Duke University alumni]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Members of the Alabama House of Representatives]]\n[[Category:Members of the United States House of Represe